# Minimal valid .tq (tq_v1): intent → requires → result → flow: (fixed order; empty flow: is OK).
# Same idea as minimal_form.tq with a shorter intent name.
# Rules: docs/TQ_SURFACE_MAPPING.md — cheatsheet: docs/TQ_AUTHOR_CHEATSHEET.md
# Copy, edit, then: torqa surface your_file.tq  |  torqa build your_file.tq

intent demo_idle
requires username, password
result OK

flow:
